# Web MVP

- Load API key rules via `fetch("./api_key_rules.json")` — do not duplicate long regex lists in `app.js`.
- Pipeline steps: register detect/redact steps; keep future features (e.g. optimize) as new steps.
- Paths are relative to the deployed site root (`web/` on Vercel); keep `index.html`, `app.js`, `styles.css`, `api_key_rules.json` co-located.
- After changing detector rules, run `scripts/sync_api_key_rules.py` before shipping web changes.
